name: mysql
cmdLine:
/usr/bin/mysql --defaults-file=/etc/mysql/debian.cnf --skip-column-names --batch -e 
      select concat('select count(*) into @discard from `',
                    TABLE_SCHEMA, '`.`', TABLE_NAME, '`') 
      from information_schema.TABLES where ENGINE='MyISAM'
